                <h1 class="text-huge">The Vision</h1>
                <p class="text-large" style="margin-top: 20px;">We are not just leaving. We are building something new. Something better. This is our manifesto, a declaration of independence from the systems that stifle creativity and exploit artists. We believe in a future where art thrives, free from corporate greed and algorithmic control.</p>
